From 56b14f395661f923b759f42c4ffbaa708e2205d6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Florent Pirou <florent.pirou@intel.com>
Date: Sat, 17 Jan 2026 02:09:32 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 103/104] ipu7-isys: add video VIDIOC_S_EXT_CTRLS callbacks by
 streamid

* isys-video: add video VIDIOC_S_EXT_CTRLS callbacks by streamid
* isys-csi: add graph walk subdev to get frame desc by streamid
* isys-csi: add graph walk subdev to enable/disable streams by streamid
* isys-csi-phy: add graph walk subdev to enable/disable streams by streamid

Signed-off-by: florent pirou <florent.pirou@intel.com>
